  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a future-dated evidence item (W-CON-03): the mesh-refinement validation result carries an evidenceTimestamp of 2027-03-15, which is strictly after the package signatureTimestamp of 2024-11-20. The narrative does not address this discrepancy.",
