      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from published FDA pump benchmark; temperature and hematocrit deviations from VAD COU envelope were noted but not quantified. Fluid rheology in benchmark used bovine blood, not human blood representative of VAD patients, representing a significant condition mismatch."
