      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for the hemolysis constitutive equation and turbulence closure was not quantified. No sensitivity analysis comparing alternative model forms (e.g., Lagrangian vs Eulerian hemolysis, k-epsilon vs SST) was conducted. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
