      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed covering inlet velocity, viscosity, and hemolysis model coefficients. Geometric uncertainty from manufacturing tolerances was not included. Pump speed uncertainty was treated as deterministic rather than stochastic, limiting the achieved level."
