    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 factors. Seven factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate that the 95th-percentile hemolysis index prediction remains below the clinical threshold across all operating points, and the team accepted the package with the understanding that remaining gaps will be addressed in subsequent assessment cycles.",
